			<h2 class="feature-title">
		  <a href="http://www.ipso-alliance.org/ipso-tab-chairman-jari-arkko-named-ietf-general-area-chairman" title="Permalink to IPSO TAB Chairman Jari Arkko Named IETF General Area Chairman" rel="bookmark">IPSO TAB Chairman Jari Arkko Named IETF General Area Chairman</a>
                </h2>
		<div class="entry-content">
			<p> Jari Arkko, Chairman of the IPSO Alliance Technical Advisory Board and Ericsson Expert in Internet Architecture, will take over the chairmanship of the Internet Engineering Task Force (IETF), the organisation has announced. Arkko&#8217;s two-year term will begin when current chairman Russ Housley steps down in March. Matt Gillmore, Strategic Standards Architect, Office of the CTO &hellip; <a href="http://www.ipso-alliance.org/ipso-tab-chairman-jari-arkko-named-ietf-general-area-chairman">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></p>
