						<h2 class="new-title"><a href="http://www.ipso-alliance.org/june-6-2013-ipso-challenge-10k-winner-announced-at-sensors-expo" title="Permalink to June 6, 2013 &#8211; IPSO CHALLENGE $10K Winner Announced at Sensors Expo (Multiple Translations)" rel="bookmark">June 6, 2013 &#8211; IPSO CHALLENGE $10K Winner Announced at Sensors Expo (Multiple Translations)</a></h2>
										<div class="entry-content">
							<p> Congratulations to Redwire Consulting! Chicago, IL – June 6, 2013 &#8211; The IPSO (Internet Protocol for Smart Objects) Alliance successfully concluded IPSO CHALLENGE 2013 today by awarding first, second and third place prizes at Sensors Expo in Chicago.  This contest was launched by IPSO in February to both promote and contribute to the development of &hellip; <a href="http://www.ipso-alliance.org/june-6-2013-ipso-challenge-10k-winner-announced-at-sensors-expo">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></p>
